# Graph/DAG — REST Client (VS Code: REST Client by Huachao Mao)
# Run worker: npm run worker:dag (from repo root)

@base = http://localhost:3000
@workflowId = <paste workflowId from start response>

### Start DAG workflow — greet branch
POST {{base}}/workflows/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowType": "dagWorkflow",
  "input": {
    "action": "greet",
    "name": "Alice"
  }
}

### Start DAG workflow — compute branch
POST {{base}}/workflows/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowType": "dagWorkflow",
  "input": {
    "action": "compute",
    "expression": "10 + 20 * 2"
  }
}

### Get run status
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}

### Get run result (wait until status is COMPLETED)
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}/result
